{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"36":"Tribulations"},"section_detail":{"36":{"hadithnumber_first":3927,"hadithnumber_last":4099,"arabicnumber_first":3927,"arabicnumber_last":4099}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3982,"arabicnumber":3982,"text":"। আবূ হুরায়রা (রাঃ) থেকে বর্ণিত। রাসূলুল্লাহ সাল্লাল্লাহু আলাইহি ওয়াসাল্লাম বলেনঃ মুমিন ব্যক্তি একই গর্ত থেকেদুইবার দংশিত হয় না।","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih - Agreed Upon"}],"reference":{"book":36,"hadith":57}}]}